TextEng: Me not like what you say!
Text: 나 네 말 마음 안 들어!

TextEng: I'd like to ask you some questions.
Me need you tell me where stuff be.
Me think fighting make you hide.
Text: 나 생각에 싸움 때문에 너 숨어 있을 것 같은데.

TextEng: I would have thought all the violence would drive you into hiding.
Text: 폭력 때문에 숨어 지낼 줄 알았는데.

TextEng: I would like to see what you have to offer.
